Spencer Charters https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spencer_Charters 0 Spencer Charters (March 25, 1875 – January 25, 1943) was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 220 films between 1920 and 1943, mostly in small supporting roles. Spencer_Charters ( March_25_,_1875 – January_25_,_1943 ) was an_American_film_actor .
